#: src/plugins/krunner-integration/kwin-runner-windows.desktop:112
msgctxt "X-Plasma-Runner-Syntax-Descriptions"
msgid ""
"Finds windows whose name or window application match :q:. It is possible to "
"interact with the windows by using one of the following keywords: activate\\"
"\\, close\\\\, min(imize)\\\\, max(imize)\\\\, fullscreen\\\\, shade\\\\, "
"keep above and keep below.,Finds windows which are on desktop named :q:,"
"Switch to desktop named :q:,Lists all windows and allows to activate them.,"
"Lists all other desktops and allows to switch to them."
msgstr ""
"Finn vindauge med namn eller programnamn i samsvar med :q:. Du kan påverka "
"vindauga via desse nøkkelorda: activate\\\\, close\\\\, min(imize)\\\\, "
"max(imize)\\\\, fullscreen\\\\, shade\\\\, keep above og keep below.,Finn "
"vindauge på skrivebord med namn :q:,Byt til skrivebord med namn :q:,Vis "
"oversikt over alle vindauge, med moglegheit for å aktivera dei.,Viser "
"oversikt oer andre skrivebord og lèt deg veksla mellom dei."
